Well, maybe a little.

1549
01:43:01,042 --> 01:43:02,708
I'm gonna put you out of your misery.

1550
01:43:14,625 --> 01:43:15,792
<i>Helicopter's approaching.</i>

1551
01:43:15,875 --> 01:43:17,583
Mr. Sellars boards first.

1552
01:43:17,667 --> 01:43:20,708
No, no, no. Mrs. Murphy,
you and your son can get on first.

1553
01:43:25,792 --> 01:43:27,167
Officer down.

1554
01:43:27,250 --> 01:43:28,417
Mechanical room.

1555
01:43:28,500 --> 01:43:29,875
OmniCorp Building.

1556
01:43:29,958 --> 01:43:31,833
<i>Roger that. EMS on the way.</i>

1557
01:43:33,667 --> 01:43:35,417
You're gonna be okay, Jack.

1558
01:43:35,500 --> 01:43:36,583
It's nonfatal.

1559
01:43:36,667 --> 01:43:38,250
Go. Go.

1560
01:43:39,667 --> 01:43:42,000
Omni-LZ Helo-1
on approach to deck.

1561
