- What?

1563
01:43:53,333 --> 01:43:54,333
Pull up! Pull up!

1564
01:43:59,125 --> 01:44:01,458
- What the hell is he doing?
- Sorry, sir. I don't know.

1565
01:44:07,000 --> 01:44:08,125
Alex?

1566
01:44:08,208 --> 01:44:09,208
Dad?

1567
01:44:12,458 --> 01:44:13,833
Ciara, David.

1568
01:44:15,333 --> 01:44:16,333
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

1569
01:44:16,375 --> 01:44:17,375
Wait.

1570
01:44:18,417 --> 01:44:20,458
- Get out of the way.
- Alex, put down the gun.

1571
01:44:20,542 --> 01:44:22,833
Ciara, take David
and get out of the way now!

1572
01:44:24,333 --> 01:44:26,000
Raymond Sellars, you're under arrest

1573
01:44:26,083 --> 01:44:27,958
for the attempted murder
of a police officer.

1574
01:44:31,292 --> 01:44:33,792
Oh, you're here to cuff me? All right.

1575
01:44:34,667 --> 01:44:36,000
Go ahead, cuff me.

1576
01:44:37,250 --> 01:44:40,083
You can't. You're not programmed that way.

1577
01:44:40,167 --> 01:44:41,417
If you go against the program,

1578
01:44:41,500 --> 01:44:43,500
the entire system shuts down, so.

1579
01:44:43,583 --> 01:44:45,851
You don't even have a warrant.
We'll overlook this little...

1580
01:44:45,875 --> 01:44:47,934
Get down on the ground and
put your hands behind your back.

1581
01:44:47,958 --> 01:44:49,458
- I'm just from marketing.
- Now!

1582
01:44:49,542 --> 01:44:51,250
Okay, yep, yep, yep. Yep.

1583
01:44:51,333 --> 01:44:53,750
Alex, we need to work together here.

1584
01:44:53,833 --> 01:44:57,167
Because I'm the only one with
the technology to keep you alive.

1585
01:44:58,417 --> 01:45:00,083
Dead or alive, you're coming with me.

1586
01:45:05,833 --> 01:45:07,125
All right.

1587
01:45:07,208 --> 01:45:08,208
Weapon.

1588
01:45:09,958 --> 01:45:13,208
Alex, honestly, I mean you no harm.

1589
01:45:13,292 --> 01:45:15,542
If I wanted to, I could
have killed you a long time ago.

1590
01:45:15,625 --> 01:45:17,559
I just aim this right at
your head and blow it off.

1591
01:45:17,583 --> 01:45:19,375
Sellars, please! Don't!

1592
01:45:19,458 --> 01:45:22,292
I mean, if I wanted to, I could
just aim this at your little family...

1593
01:45:23,208 --> 01:45:24,792
and I could just kill them too.

1594
01:45:24,875 --> 01:45:26,726
And really, there's
nothing you could do about it

1595
01:45:26,750 --> 01:45:28,000
because, let's face it,

1596
01:45:29,500 --> 01:45:30,625
you're a robot.

1597
01:45:31,458 --> 01:45:32,917
Do you understand that?

1598
01:45:37,458 --> 01:45:38,458
Alex.

1599
01:45:41,417 --> 01:45:42,458
Dad!

1600
01:45:46,500 --> 01:45:47,792
Baby.

1601
01:45:53,625 --> 01:45:54,708
Hey.

1602
01:45:56,292 --> 01:45:57,750
Hey.

1603
01:45:57,833 --> 01:45:59,708
Everything's gonna be all right.

1604
01:46:00,833 --> 01:46:02,583
Everything's gonna be all right.

1605
01:46:52,833 --> 01:46:54,250
How are you feeling, Alex?

1606
01:46:56,292 --> 01:46:57,417
I'm ready.

1607
01:47:35,292 --> 01:47:36,792
He's ready.

1608
01:48:10,625 --> 01:48:12,000
There's still no word

1609
01:48:12,083 --> 01:48:15,042
from OmniCorp parent company, OCP.

1610
01:48:16,000 --> 01:48:19,792
And although the government
says they are rebuilding Alex Murphy,

1611
01:48:19,875 --> 01:48:22,042
rumors continue to
swirl about his condition.

1612
01:48:22,583 --> 01:48:27,042
But we have obtained
exclusive video taken by cell phone

1613
01:48:27,125 --> 01:48:29,667
that shows the people of Detroit

1614
01:48:29,750 --> 01:48:31,792
may have Alex Murphy back on the streets

1615
01:48:31,875 --> 01:48:33,333
sooner than they think.

1616
01:48:35,500 --> 01:48:37,042
The real tragedy here

1617
01:48:37,125 --> 01:48:42,167
is that our president
chose to uphold the Dreyfus Act.

1618
01:48:43,125 --> 01:48:47,792
Now, I have no doubt he was
manipulated by our biased media

1619
01:48:47,875 --> 01:48:51,583
and by whistle-blower Dennett Norton.

1620
01:48:51,667 --> 01:48:55,333
<i>I acknowledge
we know less than we thought.</i>

1621
01:48:56,458 --> 01:48:58,875
<i>But I do believe
my research program is sound.</i>

1622
01:49:00,875 --> 01:49:02,083
<i>What I did with it...</i>

1623
01:49:03,875 --> 01:49:04,750
<i>was wrong.</i>

1624
01:49:04,833 --> 01:49:07,833
The fact that this mother

1625
01:49:07,917 --> 01:49:11,250
is not serving time in
some federal penitentiary

1626
01:49:11,333 --> 01:49:14,833
is a huge, hot,
heaping pile of horse.

1627
01:49:21,042 --> 01:49:25,375
Now I know some of you may think
that this kind of thinking is dangerous

1628
01:49:25,458 --> 01:49:28,958
and these machines
violate your civil liberties.

1629
01:49:29,417 --> 01:49:33,750
Some of you even believe
that the use of these drones overseas

1630
01:49:33,833 --> 01:49:38,167
makes us the same
kind of bullying imperialists

1631
01:49:38,625 --> 01:49:40,833
that our forefathers
were trying to escape.

1632
01:49:41,667 --> 01:49:43,708
To you, I say...

1633
01:49:44,625 --> 01:49:46,542
stop whining!

1634
01:49:48,542 --> 01:49:51,250
America is now

1635
01:49:51,333 --> 01:49:53,750
and always will be

1636
01:49:53,833 --> 01:49:57,750
the greatest country
on the face of the Earth!

1637
01:50:02,583 --> 01:50:03,833
I'm Pat Novak.

1638
01:50:05,667 --> 01:50:06,833
Good night.
